    <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="1">
        <title>HOOD</title>
        <para>The hood is a one piece, fiberglass sculptured, structure with bonded fender sections and an integral air
            duct. The hood is hinged at the front, latches on both sides at the rear, and tilts forward allowing easy
            access to the engine and engine accessories.
        </para>
